  "details": "A flaw has been found in kleneway awesome-cursor-mpc-server up to 2.0.1. Impacted is the function runCodeReviewTool of the file src/tools/codeReview.ts of the component Ccode-Review Tool. Executing a manipulation can lead to command injection. The attack may be launched remotely. The exploit has been published and may be used. The project was informed of the problem early through a pull request but has not reacted yet.",
